﻿​Stay up to date with what is happening in our taproom and see where you might catch us out and about pouring some of small batch craft beer!

Brew Club of Seminole County
All are welcome to attend the monthly brew club meeting. Knowledge and fun are shared by all!
/$
$
/$
$
When:
First Thursday of every month from 7 PM to 10 PM
/$
$
$
Weekdays
Between 5-7pm​
/$

Social Hour
Start your evening plans with Community Brewhouse. We add new beers every week. Stop in, get comfortable, and see what we have been brewing!
/$
$
/$
$
When:
Weekdays between 5-7pm
/$
$
/$
$
Did You Know!
Outside food is always welcome. Whether you bring it in or order it and have it delivered. We know we don't have a kitchen, but that doesn't mean there isn't great food available near by to enjoy at Community!
/$

$
When:
Anytime!

New Hours!
You can now enjoy our delicious beer until 10 pm on Thursday too! So relax in a comfy chair, or enjoy some of our retro gaming.
